descriptionHtml:
This mod adds a new set of Tifa Lockhart [url=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tifa_Lockhart][img]https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/6/61/Tifa_Lockhart_art.png[/img][/url] clothing to the game.
[font=Georgia][size=4]7Base Maximun Body[/size][/font], since I don't intend to make small melon outfit for Tifa hahahahah
Notice that this is a total re-make of Tifa clothing and is different from [b][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/12673/?]Himmelsky's.[/url][/b]


[img]http://i.imgur.com/eK1APLj.png[/img]

Install with your favorite Mod Manager or Extract the archive and drag the Data folder into the Skyrim install directory.
You need [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/26800/?]XPMS[/url] and [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/36992/?]7B Bombshell[/url]

[size=5]How to Get[/size]
Outfit: xx008edd
Gloves: xx008ede
Boots: xx008edf

replace 'xx' with your load order
